Package: picam-hailo
Version: 1.0.0+202606091437
Architecture: arm64
Maintainer: Jaco Hanekom <jhanekom@gmail.com>
Installed-Size: 227
Depends: hailort (>= 4.20.0), libc6 (>= 2.34), libgcc-s1 (>= 3.0), libjpeg62-turbo (>= 1.3.1), libstdc++6 (>= 11), picam-raw
Section: video
Priority: optional
Description: Hailo-8 NPU inference on raw YUV420 stream from picam-raw
 Receives raw YUV420 UDP frames from picam-raw, runs YOLOv8 object
 detection on the Hailo-8 NPU, and outputs newline-delimited JSON
 detections to stdout or TCP.
 .
 Requires HailoRT >= 4.18 installed separately from the Hailo
 Developer Zone.
 .
 Config: /etc/picam-hailo/config.ini
